向好，這類樓盤走勢相對較佳。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局數據顯示，去年私樓施工量大減三成六至1.18萬伙，落成量增逾五成至2.09萬伙，現樓貨尾1.2萬伙，估計未來3至4年私人住宅潛在新供應9.2萬個單位。<br />\n<br />\n蔡金強指出，移民潮對樓市構成影響，較具移民條件的中產或專業人士留港意欲降低，加上內地精英不再對香港趨之若鶩，相關需求減少，未來兩年中至高價樓會受拖累。他說：「成日有睇樓，已有啲筍盤出現。」但相信移民盤不會海量湧現，移民不代表要即時放盤，尤其業主未必願意以低於市價出讓。由於環球央行放水下資金主要流入股市、債市及黃金，故不看好樓市前景。<br />\n<br />\n【相關新聞】<br />\n【專家料樓市辣招暫不變】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NIxuFB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NIxuFB&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=a4b1e11d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2NIxuFB</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n訂閱《信報》-&gt; <a href=\"http://bit.ly/23J4bnc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F23J4bnc&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=8a112936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/23J4bnc</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #今日信報 #英國國民海外護照 #香港 #中高價樓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"幾多錢上限仍算大眾市場？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"基本上一百萬兩房一廳都嫌貴"},{"pid":"fa8166fe3435535614d3d9ddf7f1dcde9d6eb5bb","tid":2389980,"uid":244797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:31:19.000Z","msg":"林鄭奇謀黎<br />\n黑暗兵法 智冠天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37a86a28ebea69ad772ee097ef97664ba2b14a7","tid":2389980,"uid":200200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c64f8af08d6b630974fe4a6c5a552f8bb8bf52","tid":2389980,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"白鳩痴，股樓創新高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"望下恆指頭幾隻火車頭係咩股先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n造數容不易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm